metadata.title: Shard warrior
metadata.visionDescription: The image features an alien-like character with a humanoid form and an owl-like head. It is clad in a long, black robe with intricate designs. Its skin is a mix of purple and pink hues with a texture reminiscent of a lizard's scales. The character holds a black staff adorned with a trident-like top, emitting purple energy. The eyes are large and glowing, giving an ominous appearance. The robe has metallic-looking armor pieces on the front, and the feet extend from the robe, appearing thin and claw-like. The background is a gradient of purples, enhancing the mystical and otherworldly feel.

metadata.title: stingray

Surrounding the person in the water are three dark, ray-like shapes, suggesting aquatic creatures. The style is simplistic with basic lines and shading, giving it a cartoon-like appearance.

metadata.title: stingray

metadata.title: The Shard Norm

Its skin has a pastel, rainbow-like pattern. The creature is wearing an elaborate black and red armored robe, featuring intricate designs and metallic elements, giving it a regal or ceremonial look. It stands against a dark, cloudy background, adding an ominous atmosphere. The creature’s hands are positioned thoughtfully, and its eyes are focused, exuding a sense of intelligence and authority. The artistic style is detailed and has a fantasy or science fiction theme.

metadata.title: The Shard Norm
metadata.visionDescription: The image depicts a mysterious, humanoid figure with a colorful, horned elephant-like face and long trunk. It wears a dark, intricate outfit with armor-like elements and a long, flowing black cape. The figure's arms are exposed, revealing a pattern of swirling, iridescent colors on the skin. The hands are clasped together in a contemplative pose. The cloak has red accents with ornate designs, and there are metallic, geometric details on the chest. The background is a cloudy, muted grey-green, adding an ominous atmosphere. The style is a blend of fantasy and sci-fi, with a detailed and painterly approach.

metadata.title: Knife fight oh yeah
metadata.visionDescription: The image depicts two drawn characters facing each other, each holding a sword at the other's neck in a standoff. The character on the left has spiky green hair, wears a gray shirt with a green waistband, and has gold earrings. The character on the right has spiky dark brown hair, a black shirt, and also wears gold earrings. Both have confident expressions and are drawn in a simplistic, cartoon-like style with limited use of color. The background is plain white.

metadata.title: Shard warrior
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a mystical, alien-like character with a bird-like mask and large eyes, set against a purple background with a subtle glow. The figure is adorned in an ornate, multicolored robe with blue and purple hues, accented with metallic details. They wear a dark, hooded cloak fastened with a circular brooch. The character holds a black staff topped with a trident-like symbol, emitting purple energy. Their limbs are slender and pink with intricate patterns, and they rest on elongated, pointy feet, adding an otherworldly touch.
